<br>
Here's my reasoning:<br>
1. benefits over KEI:  2 extra mana/tick, 1 extra Int/Wis, 10 extra mana.  <br>
2. drawback: duration is half that of KEI.<br>
3. An upgrade (VoQ) is only 2 levels away.  I nearly always see it on bazaar for 50-60k, and it supercedes Tranquility in every aspect. <br>
<br>
So my desision is to save me those 20k, and put it towards my VoQ purchase fund.   Surely, once I start going more to places where spectrals drop, should I happen to get Tranquility as turn-in, I'll scribe it, but I won't be buying it.<br>
<br>
My question to all the 63+ chanters:  Will lack of C4 in my spellbook seriously affect my ability to function at levels 63-64, or it is more than viable to get to 65 on KEI?<br>
Thanks! <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Phantasmist, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webspan.net/~scorpio/graph/mezzed.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gumbletinkertumble>Gumble Tinkertumble</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#330000>(6/6/03 6:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=277.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.adstainer.f2s.com/Gumble.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tranquility: waste of pp?</span><hr size=1> It is definitely more than viable to get to 65 on KEI. Its what I did. I couldn't afford to buy C4, but was lucky enough to win a rune and got C5 from the turn in. To say I was happy is a big understatement. Needless to say, there is no point in the world for me to get C4 now. It would be a waste. The only way I'll ever cast it, is if I get the silk ornate tranquility legs. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=328977" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.adstainer.f2s.com/Gumble.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
