<br>
Opening of BoT/HoH...  The situation I generally observe is that with a few exceptions those able to function in a zone are quite able to get a flag.   I remember many folks I know balking at how hard PoJ trials were, and that they were being prevented from the exp heaven that's Tier 2 - until actually getting through, and discovering that fighting in there is actually harder than getting there.<br>
